{"tid":1766703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人去到呢個年紀就無奈","createTime":"2019-12-02T20:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T07:03:15.000Z","uid":58316,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"205c9b023f88645d9c5a048eed39a9eeb95adbb4","tid":1766703,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:24:18.000Z","msg":"以前一切執着<br />\n而家睇返<br />\n就問一句<br />\n其實執着黎做咩<br />\n有時諗<br />\n街邊d雀仔<br />\n乜柒都唔識<br />\n咪又咁過<br />\n係人先至發明咁多野<br />\n語言 科技 經濟<br />\n其實當自己係動物<br />\n人生會易過d<br />\n因為我地真係動物<br />\n只不過語言 科技 經濟<br />\n令我地假惺惺<br />\n一到危急關頭就暴露人性<br />\n<br />\n其實做人冇自己諗到咁複雜<br />\n就係諗得多先至複雜<br />\n但複雜未必啱<br />\n講真<br />\n做人既野<br />\n簡單又未必啱<br />\n複雜又未必啱<br />\n不如簡單d<br />\n起碼開心d<br />\n<br />\n做人既野<br />\n去到呢個年紀<br />\n已經唔再想堅持d咩<br />\n到頭來都係哂氣哂心機<br />\n到頭來一場空<br />\n好命賤命又係死<br />\n讀幾多書識幾多野都係死<br />\n其實知識真係唔係咩黎<br />\n外在往往更緊要<br />\n呢個世界就係咁膚淺<br />\n你可以不滿<br />\n不忿<br />\n但現實就係咁運作<br />\n就正如<br />\n人會老<br />\n青春不再<br />\n有d人老得快d<br />\n有人慢d<br />\n早死遲死<br />\n係無奈<br />\n但亦係現實<br />\n總之世上最公平就係死<br />\n<br />\n其實真係冇咩好講<br />\n人大左<br />\n事業洩氣<br />\n連興趣嗜好都提唔起勁<br />\n一直以為自己鍾意既<br />\n或者原來都唔係咁鍾意<br />\n<br />\n人有分好命賤命<br />\n係定律唔需要否認<br />\n不過以前好既可能而家賤<br />\n已經分唔清<br />\n太難過太教人無言<br />\n當自己係動物<br />\n係一個殼<br />\n時間會易過d<br />\n心理上會易接受d<br />\n賺到錢就使<br />\n放工食碗麵<br />\n行下海皮<br />\n等時間過<br />\n講真<br />\n其實已經當自己死左<br />\n每日都係多出黎<br />\n當去旅行散心<br />\n行下免稅店睇下野<br />\n望下d飛機升下降下<br />\n終有一日到自己<br />\n遲早所有野都灰飛煙滅<br />\n包括無奈同遺憾"},{"pid":"594c310a2b4871e5401b1eb7b06a0ba93ee89f40","tid":1766703,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77930df73fb14a72297d3b8780fe6fb5554ee25c","tid":1766703,"uid":296546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:28:07.000Z","msg":"講到死咗可以好似開心好多好似快好多咁"},{"pid":"6bb15e585232dc352b0f982c9f4aab76347e0a96","tid":1766703,"uid":225733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d153564c99c32ca7a2c3a69332c332e2663e5a","tid":1766703,"uid":249015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T21:18:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩18碎*~*@&gt;&euro;?"},{"pid":"3ce748dc06513748cee95004c6261bbdd49d155e","tid":1766703,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:34:41.000Z","msg":"pls"},{"pid":"c8480e76569db28fab00fbc050c5a2b94eaa3466","tid":1766703,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599af2c9b27fc3611945a5a7aea3490255b115a0","tid":1766703,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"詩人"},{"pid":"45b984a350569ef30fed82bda2ee7056228c6e2e","tid":1766703,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:59:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得做人好累"},{"pid":"7d1686639aade27167c2dd253ac79863c95d2844","tid":1766703,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"因為你係廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地蕭生70歲仲識好多野好充實<br />\n<br />\n你自己放棄人生又打飛機文"},{"pid":"23aaa8b27b8062a26e3d1a6e8547973749337226","tid":1766703,"uid":13804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20919f22b2740a3604026171543d07e8e0c77c0e","tid":1766703,"uid":225733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"有無興趣搞生前喪禮？"},{"pid":"9f5d2849eba4dacd3ff1f38aa42fca4a8e5a775f","tid":1766703,"uid":263840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,